This folder contains processed datasets and representative images supporting the manuscript:

“High-Throughput Reaction of Individual Aluminum Microparticles via Experimental Automation”

Files

Tested_particles.xlsx
Contains the full reaction log for 455 tested particles. Columns include particle ID, SEM-measured diameter, laser pulse count, explosion outcome, and test duration. This dataset was used to generate Figure 6.

particle_database.csv
Processed SEM segmentation output containing particle centroids, diameter, skewness, and image origin used for coordinate mapping and targeting.

particle_sample_positions.csv
Updated particle database with LM coordinates

Folders

/raw_SEM/
Representative unprocessed SEM images.

/segmented_SEM/
SEM images with SAM2 segmentation overlays.

/LM_before_after/
Representative pre- and post-irradiation LM image pairs demonstrating automated explosion detection.
